  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonk the Goblins! is Whackamole meets microgames! It's full of hectic score attack arcade action.  It's good silly fun suitable for toddlers, to intense completionists, and even insanely old people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👺 21 Different types of Gobs! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(That is what I call the Goblins) <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/7fa0d5acc19309dc158e6aefa921a6a0.webp?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/7fa0d5acc19309dc158e6aefa921a6a0.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=450 /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Microgames for each Gob! <br>Spell to bonk the Boxer Gob, Pat the Pet Gob, Follow which cup the Trickster Gob is under, and more!  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/e1c0bc13f41044e0878aafaf10b60d71.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/e1c0bc13f41044e0878aafaf10b60d71.webm?t=1728936151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 Loose and Expressive pixel art style! <br>Chunky pixels with snappy animations! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/1d8305be6e233470adcb97fb6f1840dd.gif?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/1d8305be6e233470adcb97fb6f1840dd.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚩 20+ Stages! <br>Learn how to take on each of the Gobs + Face extra challenges! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/ade1503b24bf9a0da33d0dfeabcfb326.gif?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/ade1503b24bf9a0da33d0dfeabcfb326.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💯 Endless Mode!  <br>Take all of the gobs until you make 3 mistakes!  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/c7c1917e36ffec441c9500415d603cce.gif?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/c7c1917e36ffec441c9500415d603cce.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👄 Mouth Made SFX!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some highlights include: Purring, Oof sound, and the Drum sound</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kia ora! I am Jack // nobones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the third game I have made as a solo developer and I proud of how fun and silly it is! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It'd mean the world to me if you played it.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hopefully it'll bring you some joy!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonk the Goblins! is Whackamole meets microgames! It's full of hectic score attack arcade action.  It's good silly fun suitable for toddlers, to intense completionists, and even insanely old people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👺 21 Different types of Gobs! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(That is what I call the Goblins) <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/7fa0d5acc19309dc158e6aefa921a6a0.webp?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/7fa0d5acc19309dc158e6aefa921a6a0.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=450 /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Microgames for each Gob! <br>Spell to bonk the Boxer Gob, Pat the Pet Gob, Follow which cup the Trickster Gob is under, and more!  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/e1c0bc13f41044e0878aafaf10b60d71.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/e1c0bc13f41044e0878aafaf10b60d71.webm?t=1728936151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 Loose and Expressive pixel art style! <br>Chunky pixels with snappy animations! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/1d8305be6e233470adcb97fb6f1840dd.gif?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/1d8305be6e233470adcb97fb6f1840dd.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚩 20+ Stages! <br>Learn how to take on each of the Gobs + Face extra challenges! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/ade1503b24bf9a0da33d0dfeabcfb326.gif?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/ade1503b24bf9a0da33d0dfeabcfb326.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💯 Endless Mode!  <br>Take all of the gobs until you make 3 mistakes!  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/c7c1917e36ffec441c9500415d603cce.gif?t=1728936151\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236540/extras/c7c1917e36ffec441c9500415d603cce.poster.avif?t=1728936151\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👄 Mouth Made SFX!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some highlights include: Purring, Oof sound, and the Drum sound</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kia ora! I am Jack // nobones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the third game I have made as a solo developer and I proud of how fun and silly it is! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It'd mean the world to me if you played it.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hopefully it'll bring you some joy!</p>",
